text: Ivanovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Kosikinsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 563 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 120 km from Astrakhan, 28 km from Yenotayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Kosika, Astrakhan Oblast
